title: Biden Bows to Putin
description: Fellas discuss Biden's Ukraine failures before laughing about the misfortunes of a frozen olympian and paying tribute to legendary bear, Hank the Tank. National Review's Nate Hochman shares his reporting on the struggle for freedom in Canada and Senate candidate Kathy Barnette joins the progrum for an interview about her campaign in Pennsylvania.
author: hello@ruthlesspodcast.com (Josh Holmes, Comfortably Smug, Michael Duncan, Josh Ashbrook, Kathy Barnette, Nate Hochman)
